			  <div class="card-body">
			    <p>The following types of content are not allowed on Mockering. This is not a complete list.</p>
			    <ul>
			    	<li>Make exaggerated promises, such as claiming that the audience can get rich quickly, or that miracle therapy can cure chronic diseases such as cancer.</li>
			    	<li>Promote cash gifts or other pyramid schemes.</li>
			    	<li>An account dedicated to the cash gift program.</li>
			    	<li>A video that promises "You will earn $50,000 tomorrow through this program!"</li>
			    </ul>
			  </div>
			</div>
			<a class="btn _btn_collapse_examples" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSpam" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSpam">Incentivization Spam</a>
			<div class="collapse" id="collapseSpam">
			  <div class="card-body">
			    <p>The following types of content are not allowed on Mockering. This is not a complete list.</p>
			    <ul>
			    	<li>The purpose is to encourage viewers to subscribe to the video.</li>
			    	<li>"Subs 4 Subs" videos.</li>
			    	<li>Sell ​​"like" videos.</li>
			    	<li>A video that provides the channel to the 100,000th subscriber without any other content.</li>
			    </ul>
			  </div>
			</div>
			<a class="btn _btn_collapse_examples" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseCommentSpam" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseCommentSpam">Comments Spam</a>
			<div class="collapse" id="collapseCommentSpam">
			  <div class="card-body">
			    <p>The following types of content are not allowed on Mockering. This is not a complete list.</p>
			    <ul>
			    	<li>Comments about surveys or giveaways that promote the pyramid scheme.</li>
			    	<li>"Pay per click" referral link in comments.</li>
			    	<li>Comments that falsely claim to provide complete video content. This could be something like a movie, TV show or concert.</li>
			    	<li>Post a link to a malware or phishing site in the comments: "omg just got thousands of attacks from here! -[xyz phishing site].com"</li>
			    	<li>Reviews with fake store links.</li>
			    	<li>"Hi, everyone check my channel/video here!" When the channel/video has nothing to do with the posted video.</li>
			    	<li>Post the same comment repeatedly with a link to your channel.</li>
			    </ul>
			    <p>Please keep in mind that these are just some examples, if you think the content may violate this policy, do not post the content.</p>
